node.text:
@jacobandco Mystery Tourbillon Diamond And Rainbow Index 🌈

Jacob & Co is redefining the historic mystery style of watchmaking with this latest piece. Utilising their unique hexagonal gemstones, they have created the illusion, which is the concept of Mystery timepieces.

What do you think of this timepiece?

By: @jacobandco

#millionairesurroundings #jacobandco #diamond #gemstones #watch #watches #watchoftheday #watchfam #watchaddict #watchdaily

node.text:
@jacobandco Mystery Tourbillon Blue Camo 💎

Many shades of blue sapphire create the concept of the Mystery Tourbillon in such a beautiful way, you almost for a second forget it’s a watch.

Powering this incredible timepiece are two of Jacob & Co.'s iconic triple-axis tourbillons, placed back-to-back. The first axis makes a complete revolution in 60 seconds, while the second and third axes make a complete revolution in two minutes. The power reserve for this high watchmaking movement is 60 hours.

By: @jacobandco

#millionairesurroundings #jacobandco #watch #watches #watchoftheday #watchesofinstagram #watchcollector #watchcollection #watchfam #watchaddict

Introducing the @jacobandco Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon Baguette range.

Since 2019, the partnership between Jacob & Co and Bugatti has helped push designs out of this world, creating these never before seen examples.

Jacob & Co have released many different iterations of the Bugatti Chiron Tourbillon; these examples pictured here are the Baguette variations. Which is your favourite?

By: @jacobandco for @bugatti
